description         Classic Macintosh emulator

long_description    Snow emulates classic (Motorola 68k-based) Macintosh \
                    computers with a graphical user interface. It emulates \
                    hardware at a low level, supporting Mac 128K through \
                    IIx/SE30 with 68000/68020/68030 CPUs, floppy, SCSI, \
                    audio, and networking.

